==English==

===Etymology===
From {{m|en|psyche}} + {{m|en|electronic}}, coined during the [[Iron Curtain]] decades, popularised during the [[Cold War]] by science fiction and fears of [[mind control]], and by Czech [[parapsychology]] scientist [[w:Zdeněk Rejdák|Zdeněk Rejdák]].

